            <path d="M12 17v4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        </svg>`
    },
    {
        text: "Affordable Pricing with no hidden fees",
        icon: `<svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
